# Multi-Page Admin Site Builder Enhancement

The goal is to upgrade the Admin Site Builder to manage multiple pages (Home, About, Contact, Products) instead of just the homepage. This will allow admins to switch between pages, see the current live layout, and make changes that reflect on those specific pages.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This change will transition static pages (About, Contact) to dynamic pages powered by the Site Builder. Initial content will need to be "seeded" or manually recreated in the builder to match the current designs.

